            "heading": "<p>Any Year, Any Milestone</p>",
            "content": "<p>Paper anniversary or golden anniversary, every year has its own photos worth revisiting. A personalized anniversary coloring book that grows more meaningful the longer you’ve been together, or even <a href=\"https://mycolorfulworld.art/collections/bulk-purchases\">custom coloring books for special occasions</a>.</p>",
