          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>Is there a better way to celebrate life’s great moments? So nice to see </em>birthdays, holidays<em> and just everyday celebrations ready for the kids to color and reimagine themselves. Cannot believe mys election of photos turned into something that will be treasured by my family.</em></p>",
