          "settings": {
            "openAccordion": false,
            "question": "<p>What's a unique anniversary gift that isn't generic?</p>",
            "answer": "<p>An anniversary coloring book filled with your real photos together. Upload your dates, trips, and milestones — we transform them into coloring pages you can enjoy as a date night activity. The personalized anniversary gift that's a gift, experience, and keepsake in one.</p>"
